    "title": "Korean Mobile Payment Apps for Tourists (2026 Guide)",
    "excerpt": "Confused about paying in Korea? This 2026 guide breaks down the best mobile payment apps for tourists — from KakaoPay to Naver Pay and beyond.",
    "date": "May 20, 2026",
    "dateIso": "2026-05-20",
    "readTime": "10 min read",
    "gradient": "from-teal-500/85 to-emerald-800/90",
    "thumbnailUrl": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1778466401664-145d10ea6e49?ixid=M3w5NDc5OTZ8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHxLb3JlYW4lMjBtb2JpbGUlMjBwYXltZW50JTIwYXBwcyUyMGd1aWRlJTIwZm9yJTIwdG91cmlzdHMlMjBLb3JlYXxlbnwwfDB8fHwxNzc5MzA5NTAyfDA&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&w=800&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop",
